          <li><a href="#stokes-law" class="hover:text-gold transition-colors font-medium">Stokes' Law</a></li>
          <li><a href="#factors" class="hover:text-gold transition-colors font-medium">Factors Affecting Centrifuge Efficiency</a>
            <ul class="ml-4 mt-1 space-y-1">
              <li><a href="#flow-rate" class="hover:text-gold transition-colors text-sm">Flow Rate</a></li>
              <li><a href="#gravity-disc" class="hover:text-gold transition-colors text-sm">Gravity Disc Selection</a></li>
